    {
      "id": "pattern.runtime_adapter_variant",
      "type": "pattern",
      "tier": 1,
      "title_zh": "运行时适配层变体",
      "title_en": "Runtime-Adapter Variant",
      "summary_zh": "跨 agent 运行时移植技能：契约、schema、校验器逐字节复用，运行时词汇（角色如何落地、并行怎么实现、状态放哪）全部隔离进一个 adapter 参考文件。变体因此便宜、产物跨运行时互认、整套测试电池原样迁移。同日实证：loop-constructor→Codex 移植，linter 字节相同，外部评测 PASS。",
      "summary_en": "To port a skill across agent runtimes, keep contracts, schemas, and validators byte-identical and quarantine ALL runtime vocabulary (how roles are realized, how parallelism runs, where state lives) into one adapter. Variants become cheap, artifacts stay cross-runtime compatible, the test battery transfers unchanged. Validated: a loop-constructor->Codex port.",
      "tags": [
        "portability",
        "runtime",
        "variant"
      ],
